WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 19]

01:15.360 --> 01:17.220
Let disciples of both sects

01:17.270 --> 01:19.010
patrol nearby isles

01:19.080 --> 01:20.140
to root out dangers.

01:20.550 --> 01:22.780
Humans and spirits coexist here.

01:23.750 --> 01:26.340
Shen, do not let your guard down.

01:36.470 --> 01:37.140
Tongzhou?

01:37.880 --> 01:40.060
They say Wuyue Court's techniques are unparalleled.

01:40.800 --> 01:41.620
Let me see your moves.

01:42.160 --> 01:44.620
I'd also like to see Xingzheng Hall's fire-control skills.

01:59.110 --> 01:59.810
Ye Ye?

02:00.670 --> 02:02.010
The streets are crowded with prying eyes.

02:02.470 --> 02:03.620
Why not find a quieter place to spar?

02:11.360 --> 02:12.370
Since we meet again after so long,

02:12.800 --> 02:14.780
let's find a place for tea instead.

02:15.080 --> 02:15.810
Changyue!

02:16.870 --> 02:17.850
You're all here.

02:18.710 --> 02:19.970
We just got here.

02:20.480 --> 02:23.250
So you're here for the Shanhai Gathering?

02:24.150 --> 02:24.900
Only you lot

02:25.360 --> 02:26.410
would dare pick a fight

02:26.830 --> 02:27.850
right in front of Wanxian Sect.

02:29.870 --> 02:30.410
Let's go.

02:30.800 --> 02:31.570
We'll talk at the inn.

02:31.960 --> 02:32.500
- Okay. - Let's go.

02:33.080 --> 02:33.780
- Go. - Go.

02:34.320 --> 02:35.020
We haven't seen each other in so long.

02:35.040 --> 02:35.620
It's been a while.

02:35.960 --> 02:37.090
We should catch up properly.

02:37.110 --> 02:37.500
Sure.

02:37.500 --> 02:39.560
[Duanming City Inn]

02:46.360 --> 02:46.940
Thanks.

02:47.270 --> 02:48.740
Right this way.

02:50.110 --> 02:51.410
One bite

02:51.800 --> 02:53.020
and I'd break a tooth.

02:56.320 --> 02:57.340
This is called huluo.

03:00.640 --> 03:01.370
The shell

03:01.710 --> 03:02.570
only dissolves in acid.

03:03.360 --> 03:04.090
The vinegar soaks into the meat.

03:04.430 --> 03:06.340
Add a bit of lime juice when you eat it.

03:06.760 --> 03:07.740
Makes it even more flavorful.

03:09.430 --> 03:11.220
Tongzhou, you're so knowledgeable.

03:11.240 --> 03:12.060
You even know this.

03:13.550 --> 03:14.810
Duantu may not be by the sea,

03:15.150 --> 03:17.500
but we keep all kinds of delicacies from the wilds in stock.

03:18.270 --> 03:19.220
Come to Yue State sometime,

03:19.480 --> 03:21.060
and I'll treat you to a feast every meal.

03:24.640 --> 03:25.180
Oh,

03:25.760 --> 03:26.340
Xiuyuan,

03:26.760 --> 03:28.850
I heard you ran into Yecha

03:29.150 --> 03:30.130
at White Cliff?

03:31.990 --> 03:34.500
Is Yecha really as savage as the legends say?

03:37.270 --> 03:39.130
Just a demon spirit from 500 years ago.

03:39.390 --> 03:40.130
Nothing to fear.

03:40.520 --> 03:41.530
Five hundred years ago,

03:41.670 --> 03:43.570
the immortal sects scattered his soul.

03:43.920 --> 03:45.370
This time will be no different.

03:50.270 --> 03:50.940
Jiang.

03:56.520 --> 03:57.220
Your Highness.

04:00.990 --> 04:01.530
What's the matter?

04:09.480 --> 04:10.180
By master's orders,

04:10.360 --> 04:11.970
Wuyue Court disciples will rest briefly.

04:12.270 --> 04:14.340
In two days, we'll head out with Sea Sect disciples

04:14.590 --> 04:15.690
to search for demon traces.

04:16.320 --> 04:17.410
This place is close to the East Sea,

04:17.670 --> 04:19.090
and the customs here differ from those in the Central Plains.

04:19.320 --> 04:19.980
Disciples

04:20.000 --> 04:21.770
must watch their words and actions.

04:22.350 --> 04:24.210
Avoid conflict with other sects.

04:25.030 --> 04:26.420
You should remember to watch

04:27.350 --> 04:28.660
your words and actions too, Qin.

04:42.960 --> 04:43.740
Qin, you're leaving?

04:50.200 --> 04:50.940
Well, Lifei?

04:51.470 --> 04:52.690
Did that snake give you any trouble?

04:52.910 --> 04:53.620
Trouble?

04:55.470 --> 04:57.500
Let me introduce you.

04:57.760 --> 04:59.770
This is my best senior brother at Wuyue Court,

04:59.910 --> 05:00.500
Deng Xiguang.

05:02.910 --> 05:04.060
Deng, let me introduce you too.

05:04.390 --> 05:05.860
These are all my friends from the academy.

05:06.320 --> 05:07.010
Ji Tongzhou.

05:07.390 --> 05:07.940
And

05:08.320 --> 05:08.860
Ye Ye.

05:09.270 --> 05:09.860
Changyue.

05:12.470 --> 05:13.860
You said Qin Yangling is a snake?

05:14.200 --> 05:15.180
He wronged Lifei?

05:15.760 --> 05:16.810
Far worse than that.

05:17.030 --> 05:17.980
He almost had her

05:18.000 --> 05:19.300
branded as a demon spy.

05:20.270 --> 05:21.370
What happened?

05:24.830 --> 05:25.590
[Duanming City Inn]

05:25.590 --> 05:26.740
Wuyue Court is clearly

05:26.760 --> 05:27.810
covering for him!

05:28.230 --> 05:29.300
How can you just let that slide?

05:29.830 --> 05:30.420
No way.

05:30.710 --> 05:32.250
I'm going to teach Qin Yangling a lesson right now.

05:33.350 --> 05:34.300
Alright.

05:34.910 --> 05:36.250
Once I've mastered my skills, I'll...

05:37.030 --> 05:38.300
I'll beat him black and blue!

05:38.320 --> 05:39.130
I'll show him

05:39.150 --> 05:40.740
I'm no pushover.

05:43.150 --> 05:44.420
Ye Ye and the others have already turned in.

05:44.440 --> 05:45.370
You should get some rest too.

05:47.000 --> 05:47.450
Lifei!

05:54.320 --> 05:55.130
What's going on

05:56.640 --> 05:57.540
with you and Xiuyuan?

05:59.830 --> 06:00.980
He's saved me a few times.

06:02.640 --> 06:03.330
So

06:04.230 --> 06:05.130
you've forgiven him?

06:06.320 --> 06:07.890
Do you remember The Ten Forbidden Arts of Sorcerers?

06:10.120 --> 06:11.500
That ancient book from Qingqiu?

06:14.230 --> 06:15.620
Before going to the Altar of Martyrs,

06:16.590 --> 06:18.690
he used a puppet spell to transfer my injuries to himself.

06:21.560 --> 06:23.210
So he never really wanted to hurt you?

06:26.470 --> 06:27.540
Back at Wuyue Court,

06:28.320 --> 06:29.980
I yelled at him, drove him away,

06:30.590 --> 06:31.370
and even hurt him.

06:32.270 --> 06:33.370
But he kept protecting me,

06:33.830 --> 06:35.420
afraid I'd be in any danger.

06:36.710 --> 06:37.540
My master said

06:38.320 --> 06:41.060
nothing in this world can outlast time.

06:42.230 --> 06:43.130
We need to learn to let go.

06:47.030 --> 06:47.540
Forget it.

06:48.230 --> 06:48.810
Let's not talk about him.

06:49.350 --> 06:51.660
I heard you took first place in the Achillea Bead Tournament.

06:52.270 --> 06:52.810
Impressive.

06:53.830 --> 06:56.010
Actually, I owe it to your Chiyan Stone.

06:59.230 --> 07:00.450
Xiuyuan let me have the win.

07:02.880 --> 07:03.540
I'm going to my room.

07:13.000 --> 07:15.100
Lifei is getting prettier.

07:15.710 --> 07:16.890
Even prettier than the princess.

07:18.440 --> 07:18.890
Your Highness,

07:19.760 --> 07:21.450
you're noble and distinguished.

07:22.120 --> 07:23.180
Lifei's eyes are glued to you

07:23.200 --> 07:24.130
whenever she sees you.

07:24.790 --> 07:25.890
She definitely has a crush on you.

07:26.150 --> 07:26.660
No doubt about it.

07:27.440 --> 07:29.060
Back then, you were all young.

07:29.640 --> 07:30.210
But now...

07:30.320 --> 07:30.860
Alright.

07:30.880 --> 07:31.450
- Well... - Enough.

07:34.000 --> 07:34.890
Why are you carrying a box?

07:36.910 --> 07:38.060
You said Lifei loves

07:38.080 --> 07:38.980
shiny golden things.

07:39.560 --> 07:41.660
And you had me prepare all this gold jewelry

07:41.760 --> 07:42.420
and magical treasures.

07:42.960 --> 07:43.690
Should I still give them to her?

07:54.350 --> 07:54.860
Lifei,

07:56.390 --> 07:57.180
I'd like to talk to you.

07:59.150 --> 07:59.810
About what?

08:04.320 --> 08:04.940
If...

08:07.590 --> 08:08.660
If I really am Yecha,

08:10.680 --> 08:11.660
would you kill me?

08:14.270 --> 08:15.060
You're not Yecha.

08:17.470 --> 08:18.740
You were just possessed by Yecha.

08:21.320 --> 08:22.100
I'm not even sure.

08:24.200 --> 08:25.130
How can you be so certain?

08:26.960 --> 08:27.740
Yecha is hideous.

08:28.230 --> 08:29.060
How could you be him?

08:31.710 --> 08:32.250
Lifei.

08:35.350 --> 08:36.420
Appearances can be changed.

08:37.110 --> 08:37.780
Enough.

08:38.440 --> 08:39.380
I said you're not, so you're not.

08:39.680 --> 08:40.450
No arguing with me.

08:45.320 --> 08:46.730
No matter what happened before,

08:47.870 --> 08:48.780
you are Lei Xiuyuan.

08:49.830 --> 08:50.490
You were,

08:51.590 --> 08:52.260
and you always will be.

08:58.750 --> 08:59.260
Alright.

09:01.160 --> 09:01.900
Remember,

09:03.560 --> 09:04.210
no matter who I am,

09:07.280 --> 09:08.090
I will never hurt you.

09:24.480 --> 09:26.280
[Duanming City Inn]

09:27.470 --> 09:27.850
Lifei.

09:28.630 --> 09:29.020
Let's go.

09:29.400 --> 09:30.090
I'll take you somewhere.

09:30.560 --> 09:31.490
I haven't had breakfast yet.

09:31.510 --> 09:32.260
There'll be good food.

09:32.510 --> 09:32.940
Wait,

09:32.960 --> 09:33.850
where are we going?

09:35.080 --> 09:36.210
I used the Vast Blink

09:36.710 --> 09:38.450
to have the imperial chefs of Duantu palace make this meal.

09:39.470 --> 09:40.490
Vast Blink?

09:41.440 --> 09:42.140
What treasure?

09:57.110 --> 09:57.610
Tongzhou,

09:58.870 --> 10:00.330
are you some kind of wealth bringer?

10:01.200 --> 10:02.210
So much gold.

10:04.060 --> 10:04.610
Like it?

10:05.350 --> 10:06.020
Catch it!

10:06.230 --> 10:07.610
- Stop! - Catch it!

10:07.630 --> 10:08.140
Stop!

10:08.470 --> 10:09.090
Catch it!

10:09.110 --> 10:10.210
Dig out its brain!

10:10.800 --> 10:12.120
[Shi Chengtian, Jin, Guangsheng Faction]

10:16.750 --> 10:17.490
Who are you?

10:18.060 --> 10:19.780
Dare to cause trouble on Guangsheng Faction's turf?

10:20.110 --> 10:20.780
None of your business!

10:34.830 --> 10:35.260
Tongzhou,

10:35.630 --> 10:36.060
what's wrong?

10:39.110 --> 10:39.780
Get them!

10:40.220 --> 10:40.660
Go!

10:44.350 --> 10:44.660
Let's go!

10:54.220 --> 10:54.780
Keep running.

10:55.220 --> 10:58.900
All of Duanming City is my turf.

10:59.300 --> 11:00.610
Where do you think you can run off to?

11:04.590 --> 11:05.090
Lifei.

11:07.680 --> 11:08.180
Gelin.

11:09.560 --> 11:10.180
Shi Chengtian,

11:10.820 --> 11:12.660
these two are guests of Wanxian Sect.

11:12.990 --> 11:14.380
You're harassing them in the street.

11:14.420 --> 11:15.260
What do you mean?

11:15.560 --> 11:16.850
Whoever they are,

11:17.340 --> 11:18.420
messing with my business

11:19.200 --> 11:21.260
is breaking Duanming City's rules!

11:21.830 --> 11:23.450
Even if Mr. Shen himself showed up,

11:24.230 --> 11:25.540
it wouldn't change a thing.

11:25.870 --> 11:26.900
They just got here.

11:26.940 --> 11:27.690
What rules did they break?

11:28.110 --> 11:29.970
They injured Guangsheng Faction's people!

11:31.060 --> 11:32.780
You were the ones torturing a spirit creature

11:32.820 --> 11:33.690
and trying to take its brain alive!

11:37.340 --> 11:38.540
Duanming City has a strict ban

11:39.110 --> 11:40.260
on torturing spirit creatures.

11:41.560 --> 11:42.810
You knowingly broke the law.

11:43.350 --> 11:44.570
Do you want to get run out of the East Sea?

11:46.460 --> 11:46.970
Misunderstanding.

11:47.590 --> 11:48.210
A misunderstanding.

11:48.870 --> 11:50.060
We weren't torturing a spirit creature.

11:50.590 --> 11:51.540
They saw it wrong.

11:52.110 --> 11:54.380
We were just disciplining

11:54.990 --> 11:56.490
an unruly spirit companion.

11:57.470 --> 11:58.610
I won't bother you further.

11:58.830 --> 11:59.330
I'm leaving.

12:00.080 --> 12:00.610
I'll be going.

12:01.460 --> 12:01.850
Let's go.

12:01.870 --> 12:02.420
Mr. Shi,

12:03.340 --> 12:04.450
we're just... leaving like that?

12:05.100 --> 12:06.330
Do you know who that guy is?

12:06.470 --> 12:06.940
Who?

12:07.300 --> 12:09.140
He's the lord of the seventy-six islands of the East Sea.

12:09.680 --> 12:11.540
Cross him, and you'll get nothing but trouble.

12:12.350 --> 12:12.810
Let's go.

12:12.990 --> 12:13.450
Go.

12:18.350 --> 12:19.610
Lifei.

12:22.590 --> 12:23.300
How have you been?

12:24.100 --> 12:25.020
Not bad.

12:26.870 --> 12:27.380
Gelin.

12:28.590 --> 12:30.330
What happened to Tongzhou's eyes?

12:52.830 --> 12:53.380
How is he?

12:53.630 --> 12:54.180
Is he alright?

12:54.990 --> 12:55.450
Nothing serious.

12:55.750 --> 12:56.260
Just some scale powder.

12:56.710 --> 12:58.260
A few days of rest and he'll recover.

12:59.200 --> 12:59.730
That's good.

13:01.870 --> 13:03.260
Thank you, Gelin's senior brother.

13:06.680 --> 13:07.780
That's not his name.

13:08.710 --> 13:09.420
He's Lu Li.

13:10.080 --> 13:10.540
Lu,

13:11.590 --> 13:12.570
this is my sister, Changyue.

13:14.870 --> 13:15.610
And this is Ye.

13:16.400 --> 13:17.020
Lu,

13:17.560 --> 13:19.180
Gelin can be quite willful.

13:19.590 --> 13:20.570
Thanks for looking out for her.

13:21.350 --> 13:21.780
No worries.

13:22.560 --> 13:23.380
Gelin is my junior sister.

13:23.710 --> 13:24.380
I should look out for her.

13:27.440 --> 13:28.420
I need to report the Guangsheng Faction incident

13:28.660 --> 13:29.660
to my master.

13:30.540 --> 13:31.180
I'll be going.

13:47.280 --> 13:48.180
Lu, take care.

13:48.540 --> 13:49.380
I'll come find you later.

13:53.750 --> 13:54.210
Gelin,

13:54.710 --> 13:56.260
how does a sect like Guangsheng Faction

13:56.280 --> 13:57.850
exist in the East Sea?

13:58.440 --> 14:00.180
Guangsheng Faction has always been tyrannical.

14:00.630 --> 14:01.810
They treat beasts as their property.

14:01.830 --> 14:02.780
They are absolutely ruthless.

14:03.280 --> 14:04.300
Out of respect for sect boundaries,

14:04.960 --> 14:06.330
my master can't just step in,

14:06.830 --> 14:07.780
even if he hates it.

14:08.830 --> 14:10.090
That Shi guy

14:10.630 --> 14:11.730
seemed really afraid of Lu Li.

14:12.630 --> 14:13.850
The Lu family is a major power in the East Sea.

14:14.160 --> 14:15.660
They own the surrounding islands.

14:16.080 --> 14:17.660
Of course Shi Chengtian is wary.

14:18.440 --> 14:18.900
Gelin.

14:20.400 --> 14:22.730
Does the Sea Sect treat spirits and beasts

14:22.750 --> 14:23.540
the way Guangsheng Faction does?

14:24.440 --> 14:26.060
Wanxian Sect isn't like that.

14:26.470 --> 14:28.140
We have a pact with the spirit creatures.

14:28.350 --> 14:29.490
We've

14:29.510 --> 14:30.940
lived in peace for centuries.

14:31.630 --> 14:33.140
But recently,

14:33.560 --> 14:35.180
some spirit creatures have been acting strangely.

14:36.750 --> 14:38.540
Are demons stirring trouble in the shadows?

14:42.160 --> 14:42.900
Strange how?

14:43.590 --> 14:45.810
Duanming City has been seeing many

14:45.920 --> 14:46.810
unknown spirit creatures

14:46.830 --> 14:48.180
from nowhere.

14:48.800 --> 14:50.420
I heard Guangsheng Faction caught a few.

14:51.320 --> 14:53.260
And the spirits and beasts in the city have been losing control too.

14:54.830 --> 14:55.940
Is this connected to the Sea Calamity?

14:59.280 --> 15:00.690
My master said

15:01.080 --> 15:02.330
that when the Sea Calamity comes,

15:02.800 --> 15:05.450
seawater will pour into Guixu,

15:05.750 --> 15:08.090
connecting the Central Plains to the lands beyond.

15:08.510 --> 15:11.060
Many spirits and beasts will flood into the Central Plains.

15:13.280 --> 15:14.940
Maybe there's a link.

15:18.110 --> 15:21.180
Is the strange behavior of the spirit creatures really tied to demons?

15:30.710 --> 15:31.970
Your eyes are hurt.

15:32.400 --> 15:33.730
Don't go out to sea tomorrow.

15:37.510 --> 15:38.540
Open your eyes and look.

15:41.400 --> 15:42.060
Can you see?

15:54.830 --> 15:55.300
What's wrong?

15:58.280 --> 15:59.210
Do they still hurt?

16:01.830 --> 16:02.330
No.

16:03.920 --> 16:05.060
I just suddenly realized

16:06.110 --> 16:07.300
it's not so bad being blind.

16:09.560 --> 16:10.090
That way,

16:11.990 --> 16:13.540
you'd have to keep holding my hand

16:15.630 --> 16:16.300
and never leave me.

16:41.350 --> 16:41.810
Well,

16:42.080 --> 16:42.610
don't worry.

16:43.110 --> 16:44.300
I won't abandon you.

16:44.800 --> 16:46.300
Get some rest. Don't be scared.

17:06.710 --> 17:07.850
You're here to see him too?

17:14.550 --> 17:15.290
I just saw him.

17:15.680 --> 17:16.050
Um,

17:16.880 --> 17:17.490
go ahead.

17:17.750 --> 17:18.290
See you tomorrow.

17:26.470 --> 17:27.820
I never planned to let her go.

17:30.510 --> 17:31.530
And I never will.

17:33.160 --> 17:33.730
Neither will I.

17:34.840 --> 17:36.100
Then let's each rely on our own skills.

17:37.510 --> 17:37.940
Deal.

17:44.400 --> 17:45.010
Gelin.

17:46.230 --> 17:47.290
Do you have a crush on Ye Ye?

17:53.680 --> 17:54.450
You know?

17:55.960 --> 17:57.250
Back when you cried at the academy,

17:57.880 --> 17:58.820
I didn't understand.

17:59.400 --> 18:01.010
But then you suddenly came to the East Sea.

18:02.470 --> 18:03.530
I think I get it now.

18:05.790 --> 18:06.250
So,

18:06.270 --> 18:07.450
does that make me pitiful?

18:09.880 --> 18:11.210
You've always been smart and optimistic.

18:12.340 --> 18:13.690
Why not learn to let go?

18:14.510 --> 18:15.490
I want to.

18:16.840 --> 18:17.940
But for all these years,

18:18.710 --> 18:19.290
Changyue,

18:19.640 --> 18:20.340
Ye,

18:20.710 --> 18:21.450
and I

18:21.920 --> 18:23.050
have been family.

18:23.510 --> 18:24.900
I always tried to be

18:25.270 --> 18:27.580
Changyue's obedient sister

18:28.710 --> 18:31.940
and the girl Ye worried about.

18:32.750 --> 18:33.860
But it's so hard.

18:35.270 --> 18:36.380
I thought coming to the East Sea

18:36.400 --> 18:37.820
would let me forget everything.

18:40.510 --> 18:41.580
But today...

18:43.200 --> 18:44.490
Seeing them today,

18:45.340 --> 18:46.380
I realized

18:47.680 --> 18:49.660
I'm still all alone.

18:52.710 --> 18:53.770
Why isn't there

18:53.790 --> 18:55.340
another person out there for me?

18:56.840 --> 18:58.050
I've been searching all this time.

19:02.880 --> 19:03.970
You'll find someone.

19:05.200 --> 19:07.050
At least I still have you to keep me company

19:07.600 --> 19:09.100
and listen to all this nonsense.

19:10.270 --> 19:11.180
You're right.

19:11.440 --> 19:12.580
It's good you have me.

19:12.790 --> 19:13.860
You won't be alone.

19:19.160 --> 19:21.200
[Fanghu Island]

20:00.790 --> 20:01.490
Have you heard?

20:01.840 --> 20:03.420
[Duanming City Inn]
A new man-eating island has appeared.

20:03.880 --> 20:05.210
Everyone who goes there gets eaten.

20:08.990 --> 20:10.100
Your eyes aren't healed yet.

20:10.100 --> 20:10.730
Why are you out?

20:10.750 --> 20:11.380
Go back.

20:11.920 --> 20:12.580
I'm fine.

20:13.070 --> 20:13.820
I'll protect you.

20:14.310 --> 20:14.730
Don't worry.

20:15.550 --> 20:16.450
I'll take care of Tongzhou.

20:16.880 --> 20:17.290
You...

20:17.470 --> 20:18.180
Lifei!

20:20.120 --> 20:21.860
The invincible evil-repelling talismans.

20:23.160 --> 20:24.010
Keep them safe.

20:25.120 --> 20:25.660
Here.

20:28.120 --> 20:28.970
Take them.

20:34.880 --> 20:35.660
What's that smell?

20:38.310 --> 20:39.770
It's drawn with boys' urine.

20:42.120 --> 20:42.820
Guaranteed to work.

20:45.360 --> 20:46.290
Take them.

20:46.600 --> 20:47.450
Keep them safe.

20:48.200 --> 20:50.420
I performed a divination this morning before we left.

20:50.790 --> 20:52.340
The signs were really bad.

20:52.790 --> 20:54.660
It predicted we'd turn danger into safety,

20:55.070 --> 20:56.900
but one of the divination sticks suddenly broke.

20:57.310 --> 20:58.580
It means gaining and then losing.

20:59.160 --> 21:00.010
Very ominous.

21:02.470 --> 21:03.380
What does that mean?

21:03.960 --> 21:04.660
It means

21:04.990 --> 21:07.010
even if we make it back safely,

21:07.400 --> 21:08.690
we'll still lose something.

21:09.200 --> 21:10.380
Either our souls

21:10.400 --> 21:11.210
or our money.

21:11.750 --> 21:12.180
Anyway,

21:12.640 --> 21:13.660
keep these on you

21:14.200 --> 21:15.100
for protection.

21:19.710 --> 21:20.210
Deng.

21:21.400 --> 21:23.100
Where did you get the boys' urine?

21:31.120 --> 21:32.250
A gift from heaven.

21:36.750 --> 21:37.290
It's a summoning signal.

21:37.600 --> 21:38.140
Let's go.

21:55.470 --> 21:56.010
Everyone,

21:56.600 --> 21:57.420
this island is strange.

21:57.750 --> 21:58.900
Be extremely careful.

21:59.230 --> 22:00.860
When you split up to search,

22:00.880 --> 22:01.530
if anything feels off,

22:01.840 --> 22:02.690
signal immediately.

22:03.470 --> 22:04.180
- Yes. - Yes.

22:13.710 --> 22:14.580
Be careful.

22:17.120 --> 22:17.580
Lifei.

22:19.030 --> 22:19.580
Stay alert.

22:40.640 --> 22:41.250
Changyue?

22:43.640 --> 22:44.210
Changyue!

22:45.510 --> 22:46.140
Ye!

22:52.880 --> 22:53.820
According to ancient texts,

22:54.440 --> 22:55.140
Fanghu Island

22:55.160 --> 22:56.770
is at least ten thousand years old.

22:57.470 --> 22:58.050
Who knows

22:58.070 --> 22:59.380
what strange things are hidden inside?

23:00.070 --> 23:00.970
Stay close.

23:01.440 --> 23:02.770
Don't wander off.

23:07.990 --> 23:08.580
Lifei,

23:08.880 --> 23:10.100
is that voice from a male or female?

23:11.920 --> 23:12.940
I'm asking you.

23:13.270 --> 23:13.620
Li...

23:15.960 --> 23:16.420
Lifei?

23:18.920 --> 23:19.420
Lei!

23:20.400 --> 23:21.490
We still got separated?

23:28.680 --> 23:30.660
Isn't this Qingqiu's phoenix grass?

23:30.880 --> 23:32.010
It grows here too?

23:33.400 --> 23:36.140
This place is starting to look more and more like Qingqiu.

23:39.160 --> 23:39.730
Xiuyuan!

23:40.270 --> 23:40.820
Tongzhou!

23:42.360 --> 23:43.050
Deng!

23:56.640 --> 23:57.180
Follow me.

24:20.510 --> 24:21.970
Why am I back in Qingqiu?

24:31.640 --> 24:32.340
Master?

24:34.960 --> 24:35.660
Xiaobangchui.

24:35.680 --> 24:36.770
You call this

24:36.790 --> 24:37.420
watching the place?

24:37.440 --> 24:38.940
The radishes are all overgrown.

24:38.960 --> 24:39.820
What a waste.

24:42.310 --> 24:43.250
How are we supposed to eat these?

24:45.310 --> 24:45.900
Master!

24:46.510 --> 24:47.770
You're finally back.

24:51.550 --> 24:52.730
Where have you been all these years?

24:53.120 --> 24:54.770
I've been searching everywhere for you.

24:56.200 --> 24:56.860
Kid,

24:57.600 --> 24:59.210
I had business to attend to.

24:59.230 --> 25:00.770
I told you

25:00.790 --> 25:02.380
to go find your senior brother at the academy.

25:02.640 --> 25:03.180
Look at you...

25:03.510 --> 25:04.010
Then you...

25:08.920 --> 25:11.210
What a shame about these radishes.

25:11.640 --> 25:12.380
So old.

25:12.920 --> 25:13.900
They won't taste good.

25:14.270 --> 25:15.250
What a pity.

25:15.270 --> 25:15.900
They're not old.

25:16.680 --> 25:18.050
I'll make you some radish stew.

25:21.400 --> 25:22.180
Xiaobangchui!

25:22.600 --> 25:23.770
Xiaobangchui!

25:23.920 --> 25:24.450
Run!

25:25.200 --> 25:25.970
Run now!

25:28.680 --> 25:29.380
Master.

25:29.840 --> 25:30.420
Master!

25:38.640 --> 25:39.140
Master.

25:39.600 --> 25:40.140
Master!

25:41.160 --> 25:43.490
Run... Run now!

25:43.510 --> 25:44.180
Master!

25:47.840 --> 25:48.770
Master!

26:25.120 --> 26:25.660
Lifei.

26:27.310 --> 26:28.250
It's me, Lei Xiuyuan.

26:31.680 --> 26:32.450
I was before,

26:33.790 --> 26:34.690
and I still am.

26:37.160 --> 26:38.050
You're not Xiuyuan.

26:38.710 --> 26:39.770
Who are you really?

26:50.270 --> 26:51.180
Xiaobangchui.

26:52.160 --> 26:53.140
I am Yecha.

26:55.030 --> 26:55.690
Fake.

26:57.550 --> 26:58.450
It's all fake!

27:02.200 --> 27:04.490
Mind as pure as ice, untouched by a falling sky.

27:05.070 --> 27:07.530
Stay calm through all changes; keep your spirit steady and your mind clear.

27:20.400 --> 27:21.250
What the heck is that?

27:23.600 --> 27:24.210
Stop running!

27:32.790 --> 27:34.180
A lump of green mud?

28:17.440 --> 28:18.010
Xiuyuan.

28:18.790 --> 28:19.490
Wake up.

28:20.270 --> 28:20.770
Xiuyuan.

28:21.310 --> 28:22.140
You are not Yecha.

28:22.600 --> 28:23.730
Don't let the demonic force take you.

28:24.470 --> 28:25.140
Xiuyuan!

30:17.400 --> 30:18.690
Just a mirage dream!

30:51.200 --> 30:51.820
Lifei?

30:55.510 --> 30:57.420
Did I hurt you again?

30:58.070 --> 30:59.010
You idiot!

31:00.270 --> 31:02.290
You almost got corrupted by demonic force again.

31:04.070 --> 31:06.180
Your resolve has shaken, and your sanity fades.

31:07.030 --> 31:08.690
Where's all that training Elder Guangwei gave you?

31:09.750 --> 31:10.820
What happened to all your cultivation?

31:14.550 --> 31:15.820
Where's the evil-repelling talisman Deng gave you?

31:16.200 --> 31:17.580
Did you eat it?

31:30.030 --> 31:31.100
From now on,

31:31.470 --> 31:32.340
stay sharp!

31:33.120 --> 31:34.140
If you get possessed

31:34.310 --> 31:35.380
by some ghost or demon again,

31:35.990 --> 31:36.450
I...

31:37.310 --> 31:38.180
I'm done with you.

31:41.600 --> 31:42.580
You still want me?

31:46.470 --> 31:47.770
Let's get back to Duanming City first,

31:48.160 --> 31:49.140
then we'll settle this.

31:49.400 --> 31:50.420
Otherwise, I'd be losing out.

31:51.990 --> 31:53.420
Come on, let's find the others.

32:04.400 --> 32:05.050
Tongzhou?

32:17.160 --> 32:18.940
Tongzhou, congratulations on mastering the Xuanhua Sacred Fire.

32:19.310 --> 32:20.140
From now on,

32:20.160 --> 32:21.940
[Ji Tonghe]
no one will dare bully the Yue State.

32:43.070 --> 32:43.660
Lifei?

32:45.230 --> 32:45.860
Lifei!

32:51.640 --> 32:52.210
Tonghe?

32:53.750 --> 32:54.340
Tonghe!

32:59.200 --> 32:59.860
Tonghe!

33:04.750 --> 33:05.420
Tonghe?

33:08.680 --> 33:09.340
Mr. Xuanshan?

33:12.550 --> 33:14.180
Mr. Xuanshan!

33:32.790 --> 33:33.100
Tong...

33:33.510 --> 33:34.140
Tonghe.

33:35.070 --> 33:35.730
Tonghe.

33:51.200 --> 33:51.900
Lifei.

34:00.160 --> 34:00.690
No.

34:02.230 --> 34:03.010
Don't go.

34:03.680 --> 34:04.340
Lifei!

34:07.030 --> 34:08.380
Don't leave me alone.

34:12.920 --> 34:13.490
Lifei...

34:28.920 --> 34:29.490
Tongzhou!

34:37.320 --> 34:37.900
Tongzhou.

34:39.110 --> 34:39.700
Tongzhou.

34:40.190 --> 34:40.820
Wake up.

34:41.840 --> 34:42.450
Tongzhou.

34:44.470 --> 34:45.610
Didn't that lump of mud already scatter?

34:45.630 --> 34:46.530
Why isn't he waking up?

34:47.150 --> 34:48.820
Legend says the mirage beast feeds on nightmares.

34:49.630 --> 34:50.530
If the obsession runs too deep,

34:51.070 --> 34:52.050
even after the mirage dissipates,

34:52.190 --> 34:52.970
he still won't wake up.

34:54.590 --> 34:55.380
Then what do we do?

34:55.840 --> 34:56.970
Is there a way to break it?

35:10.960 --> 35:11.530
Tongzhou!

35:11.720 --> 35:12.260
Tongzhou.

35:13.190 --> 35:13.820
Wake up.

35:14.800 --> 35:15.530
- Wake up! - Lifei.

35:16.320 --> 35:16.900
Lifei.

35:17.510 --> 35:18.700
You're back, Lifei!

35:19.840 --> 35:20.380
Lifei.

35:20.510 --> 35:21.260
Alright, alright.

35:21.590 --> 35:22.650
Whatever you just saw,

35:22.670 --> 35:23.380
it wasn't real.

35:23.550 --> 35:24.780
It was all illusions created by the mirage beast.

35:25.670 --> 35:26.340
It wasn't real?

35:28.280 --> 35:29.170
All fake?

35:30.670 --> 35:31.420
Are you fake too?

35:32.470 --> 35:33.340
I'm real.

35:33.880 --> 35:35.050
When you wouldn't wake up,

35:35.070 --> 35:36.090
I used the Fragrance Bond to come in.

35:36.960 --> 35:37.450
Lifei.

35:37.920 --> 35:38.700
It's really you?

35:39.360 --> 35:40.300
As long as you're real.

35:40.800 --> 35:41.610
Don't leave me.

35:42.400 --> 35:43.220
You're all I have now.

35:43.510 --> 35:44.420
Don't leave me.

35:44.720 --> 35:45.820
Never leave me.

35:46.190 --> 35:47.610
You're truly all I have now, Lifei.

35:47.670 --> 35:48.260
Tongzhou.

35:48.280 --> 35:48.740
Lifei.

35:48.760 --> 35:49.220
Tongzhou.

35:49.240 --> 35:50.090
Don't leave me.

35:50.630 --> 35:51.650
- Lifei. - Wake up.

35:52.840 --> 35:54.170
- Tongzhou. - Don't...

35:54.190 --> 35:55.340
Don't leave me.

35:57.840 --> 35:58.340
Lifei.

35:59.440 --> 36:00.380
Don't leave.

36:00.630 --> 36:03.130
Lifei, don't leave me.

36:04.030 --> 36:05.170
Don't leave me, Lifei!

36:05.190 --> 36:05.780
No...

36:06.190 --> 36:07.450
- Don't leave me! - No, Tongzhou!

36:07.590 --> 36:08.780
Don't let yourself be dragged down.

36:09.470 --> 36:10.090
Wake up.

36:10.400 --> 36:11.050
Wake up!

36:12.240 --> 36:12.900
Lifei.

36:13.470 --> 36:14.300
Lifei!

36:21.190 --> 36:21.780
Rise.

36:25.150 --> 36:25.780
How are you?

36:26.190 --> 36:26.860
Are you okay?

36:36.920 --> 36:37.570
Don't think about it.

36:38.470 --> 36:39.820
It's all because of that lump of mud.

36:40.150 --> 36:41.220
Everything in the dream was fake.

36:41.670 --> 36:42.450
Don't take it to heart.

36:45.840 --> 36:46.380
Someone's there.

36:49.550 --> 36:50.170
Gelin!

36:50.590 --> 36:51.170
Gelin!

36:53.240 --> 36:54.860
Changyue! Ye Ye.

36:56.150 --> 36:56.900
Are you alright?

36:57.960 --> 36:58.530
We're fine.

36:59.190 --> 36:59.740
Just

36:59.760 --> 37:01.300
saw some strange things.

37:02.550 --> 37:03.340
What did you see?

37:06.590 --> 37:07.530
We restored the Gaolu State,

37:07.920 --> 37:08.650
destroyed Longming Sanctuary,

37:09.630 --> 37:10.610
and became great heroes.

37:16.360 --> 37:16.940
But

37:17.590 --> 37:18.570
it all vanished quickly.

37:19.150 --> 37:20.220
Just a fleeting dream.

37:20.550 --> 37:21.300
Ended up alone.

37:21.630 --> 37:22.260
Not a good ending.

37:23.070 --> 37:23.820
It was all fake.

37:24.320 --> 37:25.010
Just an illusion.

37:25.760 --> 37:26.340
Forget it.

37:29.070 --> 37:29.490
Oh,

37:29.990 --> 37:31.220
have any of you seen Gelin?

37:34.150 --> 37:34.780
Gelin!

37:35.720 --> 37:37.610
Gelin!

37:37.720 --> 37:38.340
Gelin!

37:40.240 --> 37:41.340
- Gelin! - Gelin!

37:42.190 --> 37:43.050
Gelin!

37:49.470 --> 37:50.220
Gelin!

37:51.670 --> 37:52.530
Gelin!

37:56.630 --> 37:57.220
Gelin.

38:02.110 --> 38:03.010
- Gelin. - Gelin.

38:07.470 --> 38:08.860
- Gelin! - Gelin!

38:10.760 --> 38:11.420
- Gelin. - Gelin.

38:11.630 --> 38:12.530
- Gelin, wake up. - Gelin, wake up.

38:12.960 --> 38:13.650
Wake up.

38:16.070 --> 38:16.970
Ye?

38:43.030 --> 38:44.050
Are you hurt?

38:48.360 --> 38:48.900
I...

38:58.800 --> 38:59.420
Lu.

39:00.320 --> 39:01.740
Weren't you supposed to stay in Duanming City?

39:01.760 --> 39:02.610
Why are you here too?

39:07.400 --> 39:08.570
My master sent me to help.

39:12.360 --> 39:13.610
Lu, you're finally here.

39:15.440 --> 39:16.940
Are the other disciples here too?

39:17.240 --> 39:18.220
Take me to them.

39:37.320 --> 39:38.050
I'll take you.

39:43.360 --> 39:43.900
Alright.

39:45.400 --> 39:46.300
They can't see you anymore.

39:52.590 --> 39:53.610
Thank you, Lu.

39:54.840 --> 39:55.740
How long will you keep up the act?

39:59.760 --> 40:00.450
What?

40:02.070 --> 40:03.300
You like Ye Ye, don't you?

40:03.990 --> 40:05.260
Was it for him that you went to end your life

40:05.960 --> 40:06.740
at the cliff?

40:12.440 --> 40:13.530
Lu, don't joke.

40:13.990 --> 40:15.170
The one I like is you.

40:16.760 --> 40:17.820
You're the one

40:18.190 --> 40:19.860
who's always cold to me.

40:20.590 --> 40:21.490
It really breaks my heart.

40:22.840 --> 40:24.300
Are you really into me,

40:26.240 --> 40:27.050
or

40:28.990 --> 40:30.420
am I just a shield?

40:40.280 --> 40:41.170
We shouldn't stay here long.

40:41.440 --> 40:42.170
Let's go.

40:51.800 --> 40:52.380
Are you okay?

40:52.400 --> 40:52.900
I'm fine.

40:57.670 --> 40:58.700
Is everyone alright?

41:06.190 --> 41:08.700
Never thought this island held a mirage demon.

41:09.320 --> 41:11.740
They say this beast is treacherous

41:11.800 --> 41:13.050
and skilled at creating illusions.

41:13.190 --> 41:14.900
Only those with the strongest will

41:14.920 --> 41:16.050
can break through

41:16.070 --> 41:16.900
and slay it.

41:17.320 --> 41:19.570
Who managed that?

41:26.110 --> 41:27.050
I'm guessing

41:28.150 --> 41:30.170
it was Deng's evil-repelling talismans that did the trick.

41:34.670 --> 41:35.450
Where's Deng?

41:45.920 --> 41:46.780
Deng!

41:47.960 --> 41:49.170
Deng, what happened?

41:49.630 --> 41:50.300
Don't even ask.

41:51.070 --> 41:53.650
I almost got forced into something.

41:54.070 --> 41:54.820
Forced?

41:59.110 --> 42:01.970
Forced to become the head of Wuyue Court.

42:02.720 --> 42:03.780
Becoming the head?

42:06.550 --> 42:07.900
What's wrong with that?

42:09.280 --> 42:10.380
What's good about it?

42:10.630 --> 42:11.900
If you want it, you take it.

42:11.920 --> 42:13.570
- I... - Short-lived and exhausting.

42:13.840 --> 42:15.490
Why would I do that to myself?

42:15.670 --> 42:17.420
Isn't it better to sleep in and laze around every day?

42:18.190 --> 42:19.700
Wake up already.

42:19.720 --> 42:21.130
I woke up just in time.

42:21.400 --> 42:22.700
If I'd been any slower,

42:22.720 --> 42:24.650
I'd be wearing the head's robe.

42:30.190 --> 42:30.860
Qin.

42:31.470 --> 42:32.050
Qin.

42:32.400 --> 42:33.260
What happened to you?

42:33.800 --> 42:35.130
Did you get beaten up in your dream?

42:42.050 --> 42:42.750
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.750 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
